Description: # lase - Gitflow release tool
        
        
        ## Installing
        
        ```sh
        pip install lase
        ```
        
        
        ## Using
        
        Start a release:
        
        ```sh
        lase start
        ```
        
        Finish a release:
        
        ```sh
        lase finish
        ```
        
        
        ## Developing
        
        Prerequisites:
        
        - Python 3
        - pipenv
        
        
        Initialize a virtualenv with dev dependencies installed:
        
        ```sh
        make develop
        ```
        
        Run unit-tests:
        
        ```sh
        make test
        ```
        
        Run functional tests (you'll need [Shelter](https://github.com/node13h/shelter) installed to run these tests):
        
        ```sh
        make e2e-test
        ```
        
        Start a release:
        
        ```sh
        make release-start
        ```
        
        Finish a release:
        
        ```sh
        make release-finish
        ```
        
        Buld and publish the source distribution for the version X.Y.Z:
        
        ```sh
        git checkout X.Y.Z
        make publish
        ```
        
